these are just some random notes about the code

Init:

008a: ff
008b: ff


# this is probably the initial stack
# it sits above the code
sp: # 1b1b lds const
0082: 1b from sp
0083: 1b from sp + 1

M00C8: tty width, 0 on enter

0111: 00 from clr M0111 (and source FCB $00)

tmpptr:
load 0x0065 into x
